Author Overview


02 Feb 2014 00:43






Thanks to Voct, CryogenChaos, Djoric, TwistedGears, Iceforge, Wogglebug, and many, many other chat users who read through this and helped craft this skip into what it is now.

The inspiration for this came from the idea of damnatio memoriae: I was reading about the Turin King List (aka a list of Egyptian pharaohs), and a few entries were wiped out, or too damaged to read. My imagination went  and this happened.

EDIT: Oh, and the image is from the Global Egyptian Museum.





